    tag: 'Industry',
  },
  {
    slug: 'is-ai-music-allowed-on-spotify',
    title: 'Is AI Music Allowed on Spotify? What the 2026 Rules Actually Say',
    description: 'Yes, AI-assisted music is allowed on Spotify. What gets removed is spam, impersonation, and artificial streaming. Here is the real line between AI-assisted production and content-farm uploads.',
